      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/8b10aaae-c9f2-11e3-a880-52540035b04c).  Ran 19 tests.  1 tests failed: conf-sanity.",
