        "_account_id": 144,
        "name": "Hongchao Zhang",
        "email": "hongchao@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "Hongchao.zhang"
      },
      "date": "2014-04-23 08:15:34.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nIt's better to define a new function to initialize & adjust the \"cl_dirty_mb\",\nfor the current 4 cases dealing with it are almost the same.\n\ne.g.\n\nstatic inline void adjust_client_max_dirty(struct client_obd *cli)\n{\n        /* initializing */\n        if (cli->cl_dirty_max <= 0)\n                cli->cl_dirty_max = OSC_MAX_DIRTY_DEFAULT * 1024 * 1024;\n        else\n                cli->cl_dirty_max = cli->cl_max_rpcs_in_flight *\n                                (cli->cl_max_pages_per_rpc << PAGE_CACHE_SHIFT);\n\n        if (cli->cl_dirty_max >> PAGE_CACHE_SHIFT > totalram_pages / 8)\n                cli->cl_dirty_max = totalram_pages << (PAGE_CACHE_SHIFT - 3);\n}",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
